# рџ”— API Routes

| Method | Route              | Description   |
| ------ | ------------------ | ------------- |
| GET    | /polls             | Get all polls |
| POST   | /polls             | Create poll   |
| POST   | /polls/:id/vote    | Vote poll     |
| DELETE | /polls/:id         | Delete poll   |
| GET    | /polls/:id/results | Get results   |

---

# Database Schema

Poll Model

```
{
  question: String,
  createdBy: String,
  options: [
    {
      text: String,
      votes: Number
    }
  ],
  voters: [String]
}
```

# Setup Instructions

## Backend

npm install
npm start

## Frontend

npm install
npm run dev

# Environment Variables

Create `.env` file:

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection
PORT=8000

